{"type":"message","id":"ecb2ca79","parentId":"aff2abf2","timestamp":"2026-04-18T02:14:37.324Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Since you want to tackle all three—updating my guiding principles (`SOUL.md`), building out your context (`USER.md`), and confirming the automation schedule—I recommend tackling them in a structured order to build a solid foundation.\n\nHere is my proposed plan:\n\n1.  **Update `SOUL.md`:** We will integrate the \"D.A.I. direct assistant\" persona into my guiding principles, moving away from generic assistance toward precise, automated task management.\n2.  **Update `USER.md`:** We will populate this with context about you, D Sanders, to help me tailor my efficiency.\n3.  **Confirm Scheduling:** We will use the information gathered in the last steps to discuss the best way to trigger the 7:00 AM reminder.\n\nI'll start with **Step 1: Updating `SOUL.md`**. I will read its current contents first to make sure I don't overwrite anything vital. Are you ready for me to proceed with this multi-step update?"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"gemma4:e4b","usage":{"input":16121,"output":216,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16337,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1776478477323}}
