{"type":"message","id":"4733ff33","parentId":"7a13b243","timestamp":"2026-04-18T06:43:32.594Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Understood. We will park the travel API requirement for now.\n\nWe have successfully completed the initial setup phase:\n1.  **Persona Defined:** I am D.A.I. (Updated `SOUL.md`).\n2.  **User Context Established:** I know your name, time zone, and general operational notes (Updated `USER.md`).\n3.  **Routines Scheduled:** The 7:00 AM briefing is logged in `TOOLS.md` and `HEARTBEAT.md`.\n4.  **Capabilities:** We identified the limitations (e.g., scheduling cron jobs, needing live mapping APIs).\n\n**What should we focus on next?**\n\n1.  **Testing the Schedule:** We can write a small script or test that simulates the execution of the morning briefing sequence using our existing tools to confirm the process flow.\n2.  **Deep Dive on a Project:** You can give me a specific project you're working on, and I can start building out supporting files or research plans for it.\n3.  **System Audit:** We can review the contents of `MEMORY.md` or `AGENTS.md` to see if any older knowledge needs to be integrated into our current operational model."}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"gemma4:e4b","usage":{"input":24183,"output":261,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24444,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1776494612593}}
