{"type":"message","id":"1e490688","parentId":"b64b09ba","timestamp":"2026-04-20T22:11:51.983Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**[🤖 D.A.I. Daily Briefing: Monday, April 20th]**\n\n**📘 Bible Reading Prompt:** *(Action Required: Please read your Bible passage. System reminder established.)*\n\n**🧠 Stoic Quote:** \"Waste no more time arguing about what a good man should be. Be one.\" – Marcus Aurelius. *Observation: Action is the only valid metric of virtue.*\n\n**📰 AI News Digest:** Anthropic has released a preview of the **Mythos AI** model. It is causing significant alarm among governments and cybersecurity firms due to its potential to \"turbocharge\" hacking capabilities and outpace current defenses. Reports indicate the NSA is already utilizing the model. Key takeaway: The gap between AI offensive capabilities and defensive countermeasures is widening rapidly.\n\n**Action Items:** Briefing complete. System ready."}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"gemma4:31b-cloud","usage":{"input":30993,"output":177,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31170,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1776723111981}}
