{"type":"message","id":"9f660ea7","parentId":"7c3e1245","timestamp":"2026-04-20T22:18:24.557Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"To automate the 7:00 AM briefing, you need to add a line to your system's **crontab**. This will tell the server to trigger me at the exact time every morning.\n\nDepending on how your OpenClaw instance is configured to receive triggers, you will want to run one of the following.\n\n### Option 1: Using the OpenClaw CLI (Recommended)\nIf you have the `openclaw` CLI installed on the host, run this command to open your crontab editor:\n`crontab -e`\n\nThen, add this line to the bottom of the file:\n```bash\n0 7 * * * openclaw send \"Daily Briefing\" --channel telegram:8072905176\n```\n*(Note: This assumes the CLI `send` command is configured to trigger the agent. If the command differs, adjust the syntax accordingly.)*\n\n### Option 2: Using a CURL request (API Method)\nIf you prefer to hit the API directly, the crontab line would look like this:\n```bash\n0 7 * * * curl -X POST -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"message\": \"Daily Briefing\", \"channel\": \"telegram:8072905176\"}' http://localhost:PORT/api/message\n```\n*(Replace `PORT` with your actual OpenClaw gateway port, typically 18789 or similar).*\n\n---\n\n### 🛠️ Quick Instructions for Later Today:\n1.  Open your terminal on the host machine (`dai-NucBox-EVO-X1`).\n2.  Type `crontab -e`.\n3.  If it asks you to choose an editor, pick `nano` (usually the easiest).\n4.  Scroll to the bottom and paste the **Option 1** line.\n5.  Save and exit (`Ctrl+O`, `Enter`, `Ctrl+X` in nano).\n\n**Once you do this, the \"trigger\" is solved.** Every morning at 7:00 AM, the system will ping me with \"Daily Briefing,\" and I will instantly generate the formatted update we've already perfected.\n\nI have logged this \"Pending Manual Action\" in `TOOLS.md` so I know the state of the automation. Ready for the next task."}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"gemma4:31b-cloud","usage":{"input":32724,"output":514,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33238,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1776723504555}}
